    <note>Lu(5) Bi [7051] Gui's [7049] son, Dian's [8098] and Zhuan's [7297] brother, Qi's [7048] nephew, Zhi(1)'s [1284] and Zai's [1288] uncle. One father-in-law Wu(3) Jue [4010] was the grandfather of Li(2) Gang's [8078] mother. He was also the son-in-law of a Shanyin teacher, Yu(4) Yu [7407]. Zhou(1) Xiong's [7195] and Wu(3) Xiaoneng's [1972] father-in-law. His grandson Jingzhi's [3630] son-in-law, Sima(1) Xi [3745], has the same generational name as all of Sima(1) Guang's [1488] great grandsons or great grandnephews. Qin Guan, WJ, 15.4b-5a (wife #1, born Yu, who married him at age 19 and wh died in 1070 at age 27); Lu Dian, WJ, 15.12b-13a (wife #2, born Wu, who died in 1101 at age 64); Lu You, WJ, 33.4a. CBD, 3, 2649-50.</note>
